    • retrieve

      Object retrieve​(int index) throws IndexOutOfBoundsException
      Gets the data at the specified index.
      Parameters:
      index - Index of element to get.
      Returns:

      Throws:
      IndexOutOfBoundsException - Thrown if index is negative or larger than size - 1 of the list.
